node.text:
The United States Marine Corps operate two STOVL (Short Take Off Vertical Landing) aircraft. The McDonnell Douglas (now Boeing) AV-8B Harrier II and the new Lockheed Martin F-35B Lightning II. Both are extremely capable aircraft which is your favorite?! Presented in conjunction with This is Flight! 
#thisisflight #AirshowStuff #av8b #f35 #f35b #stovl #harrier #usmc #lightningii #mcasyuma

node.text:
Was pumped to finally cross another bird off the must see list. The @bealeafb TU-2S gave us a couple good view of the Dragon Lady at slightly lower altitude than it's normally performing at. 😂
Plus a little close up of the Dragon Lady office and the work attire needed to fly at 60-70k feet. 

#u2 #dragonlady #u2dragonlady #tu2s #tu2sdragonlady #trainer #highaltitude #eaa #osh21 #oshkosh #airventure #airshowstuff
